==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Persuasive
<hw>Per*sua"sive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>persuasif</ets>.]</ety> <def>Tending to persuade; having the power
of persuading; <as>as, <ex>persuasive</ex> eloquence</as>.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Persuasive</xex> words.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

