==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Persuasive
<hw>Per*sua"sive</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>That which persuades; an
inducement; an incitement; an exhortation.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Per*sua"sive*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Per*sua"sive*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Persuasory</ent>⟦br⟧
